Package ee.pri.rl.tokenizer

Interface Summary
CharacterClass Base interface for character classes.
 

Class Summary
CharacterArrayClass Character class that can be specified by suppling an array of characters that this class contains.
CharacterClassFactory Factory for creating some common character classes.
CharacterRule Rule that uses character classes for transition.
EndRule Rule for transition at the end of the input.
ErrorRule Special transition rule for detecting errors.
ImmediateRule Rule that applies immediately for given state without caring anything about input string.
NegationalCharacterClass Character class that negates the isIn() method of internal character class.
Rule Abstract base class for transition rules.
RulesValidator Validator for checking some very important properties of given input set of rules.
State Class for denoting the state in tokenizer.
StringRule Rule for transition on input string prefix.
Token Token that represents part of the text.
Tokenizer General tokenizer.
 

Exception Summary
CharacterClassFactoryException Class for exceptions of CharacterClassFactory.
TokenizerErrorStateException Exception when the tokenizer reaches error state.
TokenizerException Base class for tokenizer exceptions.
TokenizerUnexpectedEndOfInputException An exception that is thrown if tokenizer expects some more input.
